                            <p>Enter Link <b style="background-color:yellow">“http://172.16.12.44:8080”</b> in the browser or double click on the “<strong>ESS-PORTAL</strong>” Icon provided on the desktop to start the ESS Leave Application as shown below:</p>
                            <p>Link:</p>
                            <img src="~/UserManuals/images/LeaveaApplication/1.png" class="img-thumbnail" />
